tion\n  Line 183: ### AR-032-020: Multi-stage layers verification\n  Line 191: ### AR-032-021: Build cache reuse\n  Line 202: ### AR-032-022: Minimal runtime image\n  Line 209: ### AR-032-023: No sensitive data in image\n  Line 220: ### AR-032-024: Build context compatibility\n  Line 227: ### AR-032-025: Binary compatibility\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n  Line 5: Implement multi-stage Docker builds for AgentCube server components, consolidating from multiple separate Dockerfiles into 3 optimized container images: `agentcube-router`, `agentcube-workload-manager`, and `agentcube-agentd` (with `picod` sidecar option).\n  Line 51: - Agent workspace Dockerfiles (already exists in `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n  Line 147: RUN adduser -D -u 1000 agentcube\n  Line 157: | agentcube-router | router | alpine:3.19 | ~25-30MB |\n  Line 158: | agentcube-workload-manager | workload-manager | alpine:3.19 | ~30-35MB |\n  Line 159: | agentcube-agentd | agentd + picod | alpine:3.19 | ~35-40MB |\n  Line 169: \tdocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:latest .\n  Line 172: \tdocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:latest .\n  Line 175: \tdocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:latest .\n  Line 178: \tdocker push agentcube-router:latest\n  Line 179: \tdocker push agentcube-workload-manager:latest\n  Line 180: \tdocker push agentcube-agentd:latest\n  Line 240: | DOCKER-004 | Verify binary executes | `docker run --rm agentcube-router version` outputs version |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl:\n  Line 4: {{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n  Line 11: {{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n  Line 27: {{- define \"agentcube.chart\" -}}\n  Line